4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer." This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge and aims to kickstart their career as data scientists. Students will learn to build their first machine learning models. The course duration is 16 weeks, with 3 classes weekly. Classes have a maximum of 12 people. The instructors, Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena, have extensive experience in artificial intelligence and robotics. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, statistics, and more. Students will learn to create predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy and work with algorithms like Decision Trees. The course also focuses on real-life case studies, industry-standard tools, and the complete lifecycle of AI projects. The course is available in English and Spanish, and certificates are recognized by multiple organizations. For more information, visit their website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop